data.description: Pride in ownership shows throughout!  This one is so nice!!!  Located in NE Hickory within walking distance to LR University, you're going to love it!  The main level features gorgeous flooring, a formal living & dining room, a spacious kitchen w/beautiful cabinetry, a tile backsplash, granite countertops, new appliances & 2 pantries, a comfy den w/wood burning fireplace, a large primary suite & 2 guest bedrooms! The lower level features a recreation room/den area, a 2nd primary suite & full bathroom.  If you aren't already impressed, you will be!  There is a new roof, HVAC system, tankless water heater and new exterior doors!  If you need storage, the attic is floored, the 2-car garage is oversized and there is 9 x 12 utility building in the backyard.  Enjoy the change of seasons on the back deck or the lower patio.  The level backyard is beautifully landscaped & perfect for relaxing or entertaining.  A must see!
